Package: NextWordR
Type: Package
Title: An R-package/Shiny-application for word prediction
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Boyd
Maintainer: <mikuana@gmail.com>
Description: 
  A Shiny application embedded directly into the package that it relies on which performs
  text prediction based upon user input and returns word suggestions based upon a dictionary which
  was built using a corpus of data provided by the SwiftKey company.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: FALSE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    quanteda,
    shiny,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
